<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Exercise 4 - Column Layouts</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container my-5">
        <h2>4. Column Layouts & Grid Classes</h2>
        <h4 class="mt-4 text-muted">Exercise 4.1: Sidebar Section</h4>
        <div class="row g-3 mb-5">
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <div class="p-3 bg-dark text-white rounded">
                    <h6>Sidebar (col-md-3)</h6>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled mb-0">
                        <li>Navigation Line 1</li>
                        <li>Navigation Line 2</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-9">
                <div class="p-3 bg-light border rounded">
                    <h6>Content Area (col-md-9)</h6>
                    <p>This is the primary area displaying application context data dynamically.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-muted">Exercise 4.2: 4-Column Layout</h4>
        <div class="row g-2">
            <div class="col-sm-3"><div class="p-3 bg-info text-white rounded text-center">Col 1 (col-sm-3)</div></div>
            <div class="col-sm-3"><div class="p-3 bg-info text-white rounded text-center">Col 2 (col-sm-3)</div></div>
            <div class="col-sm-3"><div class="p-3 bg-info text-white rounded text-center">Col 3 (col-sm-3)</div></div>
            <div class="col-sm-3"><div class="p-3 bg-info text-white rounded text-center">Col 4 (col-sm-3)</div></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>